oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: 11 Year Anniversary of Billy Block's Western Beat (Sep. 5)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Waldman, Wendy; Lowen and Navarro (Musical group); Bum Steers (Musical group); Fuller, Jerry, 1938-; McCue, Anne; Cunningham, Eddie; Berghoff, Ed, 1952-; Split fountain printing; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (black on split fountain, yellow to blue) announcing the 11 Year Anniversary of Billy Block's Western Beat American Music Showcase featuring Wendy Waldman, Kenny Edwards, Lowen and Navarro, The Bum Steers, Harmony Ranch, Jerry Fuller, Anne McCue, Mark Islam, Eddie Cunningham, Paul Marshall, Judy Toy, Mojo Monkeys, Jenny Yates, Ed Berghoff, and Craig Lackey hosted by Billy Block at Highland Ground in Hollywood, California on September 5. Poster features a metal photoplate of the Western Beat logo.
